headline: Robotics Transforms Cell Therapy: Multiply Labs Drives Staggering 74% Cost Reduction, Unlocking Global Patient Access
summary: SAN FRANCISCO, August 21, 2025--Leveraging Universal Robots, Multiply Labs reduces cost of life-saving cell therapies by 74%, enables 100x more patient doses per sq ft of cleanroom.
